configuring vim on new computer:

1. Add colorschemes manually (vundle fails for some reason):
    $ mkdir ~/.vim
    $ git clone https://github.com/flazz/vim-colorschemes ~/.vim

2. clone vundle:
    $ git clone https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim

3. create symlinks to connect everything by running "create_symlink.sh" script.

4. launch vundle to install all plugins: 
    $ vim +PluginInstall +qall
